description:
Fixierung der Vor / Zurück - Buttons
The fixation Back & Forward buttons

Zwischenräume sowie Höhe können nachjustiert werden
Interstices and height can be adjusted

#forward-button {margin: 2px 0px 0px 12px !important;}
#back-button {margin: 2px 0px 0px 1px !important;}

Sollte jemand den Dropmarker brauchen, muss man diese Zeile löschen
If someone has the Dropmarker need, you must delete this line

#back-forward-dropmarker {display: none !Important;}

css:
#forward-button {margin: 2px 0px 0px 12px !important;}
#back-button {margin: 2px 0px 0px 1px !important;}

#back-forward-dropmarker{display: none !Important;} 
#back-button .toolbarbutton-menubutton-dropmarker,
#forward-button .toolbarbutton-menubutton-dropmarker {display: none !important;}

#back-button {-moz-image-region:rect(0px, 24px, 24px, 0px)!important; 
list-style-image:url(chrome://browser/skin/Toolbar.png) !important;}

#forward-button{-moz-image-region:rect(0px,48px,24px,24px)!important;
list-style-image:url(chrome://browser/skin/Toolbar.png) !important;}

#back-button:hover {-moz-image-region: rect(24px, 24px, 48px, 0px) !important;}
#forward-button:hover {-moz-image-region: rect(24px, 48px, 48px, 24px) !important;}
#back-button[disabled=true] {-moz-image-region: rect(48px, 24px, 72px, 0px) !important;}
#forward-button[disabled=true] {-moz-image-region: rect(48px, 48px, 72px, 24px) !important;}
